Cookie Storage:

![alt text](image.png)
Security: XSS, CSRF

On server we can clear the cookie or storage with a header called 'Clear-Site-Data'.

app.get('/logout', (req, res) => {
    res.setHeader('Clear-Site-Data', '"cache", "cookies", "storage"')
    res.redirect('/');
})

Refer: https://github.com/namastedev/namaste-frontend-system-design/blob/master/Databases%26Caching/cookieStorage/public/index.html